  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0da2\u0dda.\u0dc0\u0dd3.\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u200c\u0da7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"JV Piya is winning the hearts of the people\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaking about a meeting with Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake, the American Ambassador to Sri Lanka Mrs. Julie Chang said that the JVP is a party that is growing day by day in Sri Lanka with the approval of the people.",
        "Mrs. Julie Chang stated that a very effective and honest discussion was held between the American Ambassador to Sri Lanka Mrs. Julie Chang and the leader of Janata Vimukthi Peramuna Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake.",
        "Mrs. Julie Chung said that if there is a problem regarding the investment in the United States and the foreign policy of the United States or if she needs an explanation, she told Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake to give her a phone call. Mrs. Julie said that then she will have the opportunity to distance herself from the false information circulating through social media and rumours. declared.",
        "Ambassador Julie Chang said that although there have been controversial situations with the JVP in the past, she felt it was her duty to meet Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake as an individual and not as a representative of the United States of America.",
        "In that meeting, she said that she felt JVP was a political party that Sri Lanka needed and that JVP would socialize their ideologies and said that this was not the opinion of the United States of America but her personal opinion."
      ],
